## Default/English email template for tasks reminder
## Notification properties: veriniceserver-plain.properties
## Notification configuration: veriniceserver-plain.xml, veriniceserver-jbpm.xml
## Notifications are send as plain text, don't use HTML.
## Save this file UTF-8 encoded.
##
## Notifications service sets variables:
## ${address}: Mr, Mrs or if not set Mrs/Mr
## ${name}: Surname
## ${url}: Url to task site of verinice.WEB
## ${email}: Recipient 
## ${emailFrom}: Sender
## ${replyTo}: reply to email
## ${taskTitle}: Title of task
## ${taskDescription}: Description of task 
## ${elementTitle}: Title of affected element
##
Dear ${address} ${name},<br/>
<br/>
this is a reminder for your verinice task: <br/>
<br/>
${taskTitle}<br/>
<br/>
${taskDescription}<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
The tasks affects the following object in verinice:<br/>
${elementTitle}<br/>
<br/>
You will find a list with all your task here:<br/>
<a href="${url}">${url}</a><br/>
<br/>
After logged in you can edit your tasks in the browser.<br/>
<br/>
[This e-mail has been automatically generated.]<br/>
